bundle install

link_to can also take a bock, allowing you to provide more complex content for the link:

<%= link_to 'My Site', 'http://mysite.com' %>

<%= link_to 'http://mysite.com' do %>
    <%= image_tag 'http://www.ldoceonline.com/media/english/illustration/skull.jpg' %>
<% end %>

Specify that the link is a relative path
<%= link_to 'About', '/about.html', :relative => true %>

https://middlemanapp.com/basics/helper-methods/